data.enText: a device that connects one computer system to another using a telephone line so that data can be sent

tr: (from a combination of MOdulate and DEModulate) electronic equipment consisting of a device used to connect computers by a telephone line

value.def: A modem is a device which uses a telephone line to connect computers or computer systems.

example.ex: He sent his work to his publishers by modem.
example.tran: 他通过网络把作品发给了出版商。
